. These false rumors caused the prices of the subject companies=E2=80=99 se=
curities to rise temporarily. Between January 2018 and January 2020, Melnic=
k allegedly spread and/or traded around the false rumors over 100 times, ge=
nerating more than $374,000 in illicit profits. The other scheme participan=
ts also traded around the false rumors, generating significant profits.I do=
n=E2=80=99t know, there is just something pure and strange about selling pe=
