ottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid;=
 background-color: #ccc;"> primary victim of the company=E2=80=99s action</=
a> is not the shareholders but some other identifiable group =E2=80=94 shar=
eholders will sue it for securities fraud. In the old, classic theory, the =
company was doing bad things to other stakeholders (employees, customers, t=
he environment)=C2=A0<em>to make money for shareholders</em>; the other sta=
keholders might sue the company for the bad things, but the amoral profit-m=
aximizing shareholders would say =E2=80=9Cgood for you, exploit more worker=
s to make money for us.=E2=80=9D In the new theory, the shareholders say =
=E2=80=9Cit is bad for the long-term value of our shares when you do bad th=
ings to other people, so=C2=A0<em>we=C2=A0</em>will sue you for doing bad t=
hings to other people.=E2=80=9D The shareholders assume that the externalit=
ies will be internalized, that the harms that the company does to others wi=
ll be revisited on the company, which will lower the value of their shares.=
 So the stock price falls and the shareholders sue.</p><p style=3D"margin: =
16px 0;">This theory =E2=80=94=C2=A0whether it=E2=80=99s about ESG investin=
g or everything-is-securities-fraud =E2=80=94=C2=A0has to=C2=A0assume<em>=
=C2=A0</em>some mechanism for the future internalizing of externalities.[4]=
 A claim like =E2=80=9C80% of hydrocarbons will be stranded=E2=80=9D is ess=
entially a claim about the future path of regulation, something like =E2=80=
=9Cif the world wants to avoid warming by more than 2 degrees, governments =
will need to impose strict limits on hydrocarbons, and the world does want =
that so the governments will do that.=E2=80=9D A claim like =E2=80=9Cshareh=
olders are harmed by Facebook putting profits over safety=E2=80=9D is a vag=
uer claim about regulation or consumer choices, <a href=3D"https://link.mai=
l.bloombergbusiness.com/click/25230754.274064/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb=
20vMjAyMS8xMC8wNC90ZWNobm9sb2d5L2ZhY2Vib29rLWZpbGVzLmh0bWw/607f07ceef4b8524=
