etter) and say =E2=80=9Chey I=E2=80=99m gonna publish fake rumors about thi=
s company to make its stock go up.=E2=80=9D</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bott=
om: 5px;">Your subscribers buy the stock and it goes up.</li>=09<li style=
