of the subject companies=E2=80=99 securities to rise temporarily. Between J=
anuary 2018 and January 2020, Melnick allegedly spread and/or traded around=
 the false rumors over 100 times, generating more than $374,000 in illicit =
profits. The other scheme participants also traded around the false rumors,=
 generating significant profits.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0=
